1
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:35,719
The remaining nine

2
00:01:36,799 --> 00:01:38,920
are governed by your men.

3
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,040
No one's spoken to me like that

4
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:05,120
in quite some time.

5
00:02:08,159 --> 00:02:09,439
Pardon my frankness, my lord.

6
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:11,199
When a man

7
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,879
has just cheated death,

8
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,479
he finds

9
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:18,360
he has very little left to fear.

10
00:02:31,599 --> 00:02:33,000
Did you imagine

11
00:02:33,879 --> 00:02:35,319
those words would

12
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:37,039
cost you your life?

13
00:02:40,039 --> 00:02:40,919
No.

14
00:02:41,319 --> 00:02:43,000
Quite the opposite.

15
00:02:44,599 --> 00:02:46,199
You have served me well.

16
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:50,360
I value a man who

17
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,680
tells me

18
00:02:53,039 --> 00:02:54,240
what I don't

19
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:55,800
want to hear.

20
00:02:56,439 --> 00:02:57,080
You're

21
00:02:57,439 --> 00:03:00,120
exactly the kind of voice I need.

22
00:03:01,439 --> 00:03:02,159
Truly!

23
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,759
Now get well.

24
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:08,719
The reforms

25
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,240
are underway.

26
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:11,800
The empire needs you.

27
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,879
So do I.

28
00:03:14,919 --> 00:03:15,840
His Majesty has ordered

29
00:03:15,919 --> 00:03:18,199
a full inquiry into the case.

30
00:03:19,039 --> 00:03:20,319
Should Wang Xuanfan

31
00:03:20,319 --> 00:03:22,159
prove to be the hand behind it,

32
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:24,039
no office, however high,

33
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:28,159
shall bring him to justice.

34
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,039
Gratitude, my lord.

35
00:03:32,039 --> 00:03:33,360
See that you rest.

36
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:35,680
I shall take my leave.

37
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,000
Safe travels, my lord.

38
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:02,080
I saw

39
00:04:02,319 --> 00:04:03,759
Lord Fu leave just now.

40
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,319
His expression was grim.

41
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:07,280
Was there discord between you?

42
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:09,919
He bade me

43
00:04:09,919 --> 00:04:11,680
put aside my grudge against Wang.

44
00:04:12,039 --> 00:04:13,560
I refused him plainly.

45
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:15,120
I had thought

46
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,920
he might intercede on Wang's behalf,

47
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:20,360
yet I did not foresee,

48
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,279
he would shield him

49
00:04:23,279 --> 00:04:24,720
to such a degree.

50
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:28,839
I told him plainly:

51
00:04:29,519 --> 00:04:30,600
six of the regions

52
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,839
where corruption took root

53
00:04:32,879 --> 00:04:34,319
are governed by Wang's men.

54
00:04:35,319 --> 00:04:36,839
His reply? Merely that they had

55
00:04:37,399 --> 00:04:38,920
"gone a little too far."

56
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,360
It beggars belief.

57
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,000
Was that

58
00:04:45,759 --> 00:04:46,680
truly worth

59
00:04:47,439 --> 00:04:48,959
the confrontation?

60
00:04:50,959 --> 00:04:52,240
I had to test how far

61
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:54,120
he would shield Wang.

62
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,680
And the test has yielded

63
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,000
its answer.

64
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:03,000
His bonds with Wang run deeper

65
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:05,160
than I ever reckoned.

66
00:05:07,079 --> 00:05:08,160
Then we must

67
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:10,560
remain vigilant from now on.

68
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,680
Not only your affairs at court,

69
00:05:14,519 --> 00:05:15,600
but my dealings as well.

70
00:05:16,399 --> 00:05:16,920
Nothing can be

71
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,160
left to chance.

72
00:05:19,879 --> 00:05:21,439
I should send word

73
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,120
to Grandmother

74
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:24,600
and Yao at once.

75
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:32,959
Perhaps

76
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,360
we should return to Tongzhou.

77
00:05:45,439 --> 00:05:47,720
Ungrateful cur!

78
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:50,399
He dares rebuke me to my face!

79
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:53,680
He'd lay the blame for those breaches

80
00:05:53,879 --> 00:05:55,040
at my feet!

81
00:05:55,439 --> 00:05:56,439
Such insolent words!

82
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:57,600
Has he forgotten his place?

83
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:58,759
It was a threat.

84
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,600
If I do not remove Wang,

85
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,560
he will unleash an investigation.

86
00:06:03,839 --> 00:06:04,319
And when he does,

87
00:06:04,319 --> 00:06:05,519
it won't just be Wang who falls.

88
00:06:06,199 --> 00:06:07,720
Half the court gets buried.

89
00:06:08,879 --> 00:06:09,519
My lord, please...

90
00:06:19,399 --> 00:06:20,920
He holds the purse strings.

91
00:06:22,399 --> 00:06:23,800
Should he choose open war,

92
00:06:26,839 --> 00:06:28,040
I have no means to stop him.

93
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:32,279
Zhang Qi!

94
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:37,800
Lord Fu asks that

95
00:06:38,319 --> 00:06:40,759
you withdraw for now.

96
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:42,759
Return home and lay low.

97
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:44,759
When the storm has passed,

98
00:06:44,959 --> 00:06:45,959
we shall arrange your return.

99
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,600
If that is
Lord Fu's wish,

100
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,360
I shall comply.

101
00:07:28,319 --> 00:07:29,680
Mind your step.

102
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,519
So many crates.

103
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,480
What's

104
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:40,519
inside?

105
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,160
Records from

106
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,720
the bureau,

107
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,519
though they date back ten years now.

108
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:47,639
When Prince Chengqing rebelled,

109
00:07:48,319 --> 00:07:49,800
he sought leverage over the officials.

110
00:07:50,199 --> 00:07:51,319
So he bribed his way

111
00:07:51,519 --> 00:07:52,120
into the bureau

112
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,399
and had every record of conduct

113
00:07:53,759 --> 00:07:54,600
seized and shipped away.

114
00:07:54,879 --> 00:07:56,399
The Cabinet had pirates

115
00:07:56,639 --> 00:07:58,160
seize the convoy.

116
00:07:59,199 --> 00:08:00,639
I managed to move

117
00:08:00,959 --> 00:08:01,720
everything here.

118
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:04,000
Can records so old

119
00:08:04,319 --> 00:08:05,519
still serve any purpose?

120
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:06,600
They can.

121
00:08:07,839 --> 00:08:09,439
A man's deeds

122
00:08:09,959 --> 00:08:11,199
always leave traces behind.

123
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,240
When Lord Fu

124
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,959
entered the Cabinet,

125
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,319
he was

126
00:08:22,839 --> 00:08:24,480
an idealist.

127
00:08:25,319 --> 00:08:25,920
But

128
00:08:26,319 --> 00:08:27,800
these files

129
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:28,439
taught me

130
00:08:29,399 --> 00:08:30,319
something else about him:

131
00:08:30,759 --> 00:08:31,920
he prizes results

132
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,399
over integrity.

133
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,120
Why is it

134
00:08:37,399 --> 00:08:38,759
scarcely half full?

135
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:41,080
I've read all of Lord Fu's records

136
00:08:41,759 --> 00:08:43,279
and retained what I require.

137
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:46,080
I presume you've studied

138
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,320
Wang's files as well?

139
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:49,279
Not a single minister of note

140
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:50,519
has been left untouched.

141
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,519
How do you intend to proceed?

142
00:08:58,840 --> 00:08:59,559
Whatever Wang

143
00:08:59,559 --> 00:09:01,519
holds over Lord Fu

144
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,320
must be truly damning.

145
00:09:03,399 --> 00:09:04,440
Nothing less could drive him

146
00:09:04,759 --> 00:09:05,519
to protect Wang this far.

147
00:09:07,759 --> 00:09:08,759
Treason?

148
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:11,159
Could Lord Fu have been in league

149
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:13,240
with Prince Chengqing?

150
00:09:13,679 --> 00:09:14,559
It's possible.

151
00:09:15,879 --> 00:09:17,559
But everything here

152
00:09:18,039 --> 00:09:19,320
only covers Prince Glorian.

153
00:09:29,519 --> 00:09:30,279
I studied

154
00:09:30,279 --> 00:09:31,720
his records

155
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:34,000
before I dealt with

156
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,000
his heir.

157
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:36,639
Right about here.

158
00:09:39,919 --> 00:09:40,399
There.

159
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:50,879
Jingning Era, Year twenty fourth,

160
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:53,679
Li Zhi summoned the Soulguide Liu Heng

161
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:56,279
to pray for his late mother.

162
00:09:56,799 --> 00:09:58,639
In attendance were

163
00:09:58,799 --> 00:10:00,159
Zhou Feng,

164
00:10:00,279 --> 00:10:01,519
steward to Prince Chengqing,

165
00:10:01,519 --> 00:10:02,799
and Wang Nianen, steward to Wang Xuanfan.

166
00:10:03,759 --> 00:10:05,159
Afterward,

167
00:10:05,159 --> 00:10:06,919
Wang Nianen sent prayer beads,

168
00:10:07,679 --> 00:10:09,799
tangerines, pears

169
00:10:11,039 --> 00:10:13,120
to the residence of

170
00:10:14,559 --> 00:10:15,840
Grand Secretariat Fu Hailian.

171
00:10:18,879 --> 00:10:20,000
Who is

172
00:10:20,159 --> 00:10:21,080
Liu Heng?

173
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:31,919
Have you heard of

174
00:10:32,879 --> 00:10:33,879
the Chunyuan Sect?

175
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:22,399
Someone cast a stone
over the wall.

176
00:11:23,759 --> 00:11:24,879
This spell was tied to it.

177
00:11:43,279 --> 00:11:44,559
You think it's Wang Xuanfan?

178
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:49,279
Who else would it be?

179
00:11:49,759 --> 00:11:51,039
He's getting reckless!

180
00:11:54,399 --> 00:11:56,000
Men with power

181
00:11:56,519 --> 00:11:57,879
rarely let go of it gracefully.

182
00:11:58,799 --> 00:12:00,360
My lord, my lady,

183
00:12:01,159 --> 00:12:02,639
word has come from the palace.

184
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:05,519
His Majesty has summoned Ye Xian

185
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:07,240
to lead the investigation

186
00:12:07,519 --> 00:12:08,960
into Chen Yanyun's assassination.

187
00:12:10,159 --> 00:12:10,759
My lord,

188
00:12:11,519 --> 00:12:12,519
Ye Xian has never

189
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:14,039
shown us any goodwill.

190
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:34,519
[By His Majesty's decree:]

191
00:12:34,519 --> 00:12:36,120
[the investigation into]

192
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:38,039
[the assault upon Lord Chen]

193
00:12:38,039 --> 00:12:39,960
[is now entrusted to Ye Xian.]

194
00:12:40,159 --> 00:12:42,519
[Ye Xian is to return]

195
00:12:42,559 --> 00:12:43,759
[to the capital forthwith.]

196
00:12:44,039 --> 00:12:45,200
Faster!

197
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:46,559
Valuables are

198
00:12:46,559 --> 00:12:47,320
to be packed separately!

199
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:48,960
Mind the fragile pieces!

200
00:12:52,519 --> 00:12:53,159
Careful!
Stop dawdling!

201
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:55,039
- You brought this on us!
- Faster!

202
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:56,080
You and your obsession

203
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:57,240
with destroying

204
00:12:57,399 --> 00:12:59,000
Chen Yanyun!

205
00:13:04,039 --> 00:13:05,919
Say something!

206
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,519
This has nothing to do with us...

207
00:13:09,519 --> 00:13:10,679
Have you quite finished?

208
00:13:10,879 --> 00:13:12,039
Don't you raise your voice at me!

209
00:13:12,039 --> 00:13:12,919
You want to
blame someone?

210
00:13:13,879 --> 00:13:14,720
Blame yourself!

211
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:15,799
Take your rage out on someone else!

212
00:13:15,799 --> 00:13:16,559
Hold your tongue!

213
00:13:16,840 --> 00:13:18,840
Good heavens!

214
00:14:51,519 --> 00:14:52,360
What did you find?

215
00:14:55,519 --> 00:14:56,120
Hey!

216
00:14:56,919 --> 00:14:58,080
What's that for?

217
00:15:00,639 --> 00:15:01,919
So the wound is real after all.

218
00:15:02,519 --> 00:15:02,960
It's nothing.
Thought you might be

219
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:04,720
faking it.

220
00:15:06,679 --> 00:15:07,360
Enough.

221
00:15:10,919 --> 00:15:11,720
Tell me,

222
00:15:12,519 --> 00:15:13,360
how many are dead?

223
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:14,840
Three.

224
00:15:15,519 --> 00:15:16,720
The Wangs,

225
00:15:17,159 --> 00:15:18,279
and their steward.

226
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:22,519
Wang Nianen?

227
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:24,679
How did you know?

228
00:15:29,279 --> 00:15:30,240
Take me there.

229
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:43,720
The Wangs

230
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:45,159
succumbed to charcoal fumes.

231
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:46,279
But the steward

232
00:15:46,279 --> 00:15:47,360
was strangled.

233
00:15:47,879 --> 00:15:48,320
He clearly

234
00:15:48,320 --> 00:15:50,000
fought for his life.

235
00:15:50,799 --> 00:15:52,120
They all died

236
00:15:52,159 --> 00:15:52,879
between

237
00:15:52,879 --> 00:15:54,440
midnight and dawn.

238
00:16:02,159 --> 00:16:03,519
Any clues

239
00:16:04,159 --> 00:16:05,200
on the steward?

240
00:16:06,240 --> 00:16:07,279
Your intuition is keen, my lord.

241
00:16:07,639 --> 00:16:08,200
Behold.

242
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:17,200
The steward caused

243
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:19,120
the Wangs' suffocation.

244
00:16:20,080 --> 00:16:21,399
Yet, he himself

245
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:23,120
was murdered.

246
00:16:24,679 --> 00:16:25,840
Any other findings?

247
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:34,200
Why is there

248
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:35,960
a cut?

249
00:16:36,559 --> 00:16:37,320
My lady,

250
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:38,799
this appears

251
00:16:39,039 --> 00:16:40,720
to be a nail scratch

252
00:16:41,080 --> 00:16:42,679
from his own thumb.

253
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:45,200
How odd…

254
00:16:45,600 --> 00:16:47,200
Why would he scratch himself?

255
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:48,559
And

256
00:16:48,879 --> 00:16:49,879
in that exact spot, of all places?

257
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:02,919
Now I recall…

258
00:17:04,039 --> 00:17:04,599
He was found

259
00:17:04,599 --> 00:17:05,759
sitting on the ground

260
00:17:06,279 --> 00:17:07,160
with his left hand

261
00:17:08,039 --> 00:17:09,519
clenched in

262
00:17:10,039 --> 00:17:11,039
a rather peculiar pose.

263
00:17:11,759 --> 00:17:12,839
Moving the body

264
00:17:13,200 --> 00:17:14,279
must have disturbed it.

265
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:16,519
Can you replicate the pose?

266
00:17:18,119 --> 00:17:19,279
It was...

267
00:17:20,559 --> 00:17:21,160
sort of like this.

268
00:17:28,599 --> 00:17:29,440
The Chunyuan Sect!

269
00:17:31,440 --> 00:17:32,240
The Chunyuan Sect...

270
00:17:36,039 --> 00:17:37,200
Have you searched

271
00:17:37,200 --> 00:17:38,200
the entire estate?

272
00:17:40,279 --> 00:17:41,720
Every corner.

273
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:43,400
You have a lead?

274
00:17:44,119 --> 00:17:45,200
I suspect as much.

275
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:47,759
But I need to

276
00:17:51,519 --> 00:17:52,880
prove it.

277
00:17:55,559 --> 00:17:57,319
Lord Chen attacked,

278
00:17:57,319 --> 00:17:58,559
the Wangs dead

279
00:17:58,559 --> 00:17:59,559
in their own manor!

280
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:02,079
These men were the pillars of my throne.

281
00:18:02,759 --> 00:18:04,039
Has the capital

282
00:18:04,039 --> 00:18:05,200
fallen into such chaos?

283
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:06,079
Your Majesty,

284
00:18:06,559 --> 00:18:09,119
it's more than a failure of law.

285
00:18:09,319 --> 00:18:10,119
Continue, my lord.

286
00:18:11,200 --> 00:18:12,119
Lord Wang

287
00:18:12,720 --> 00:18:13,880
was my aide

288
00:18:14,119 --> 00:18:15,799
for years;

289
00:18:16,160 --> 00:18:16,920
Yanyun

290
00:18:17,839 --> 00:18:19,319
is my protégé.

291
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:21,400
The mystery

292
00:18:21,720 --> 00:18:22,920
runs deep,

293
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:25,079
and many fear to tread here.

294
00:18:25,079 --> 00:18:26,119
Let me

295
00:18:27,039 --> 00:18:28,319
take up this burden myself.

296
00:18:40,160 --> 00:18:41,079
Lord Wang!

297
00:18:43,480 --> 00:18:44,359
My lord?

298
00:18:44,960 --> 00:18:47,519
You uncovered that

299
00:18:47,759 --> 00:18:49,319
Wang Xuanfan had

300
00:18:49,319 --> 00:18:50,799
Chen Yanyun shadowed,

301
00:18:51,519 --> 00:18:52,240
correct?

302
00:18:52,480 --> 00:18:53,640
Yes, my lord.

303
00:18:54,839 --> 00:18:55,880
The man confessed that

304
00:18:56,319 --> 00:18:58,559
Wang feared Chen would

305
00:18:58,720 --> 00:18:59,480
expose his ties

306
00:18:59,480 --> 00:19:01,039
to Prince Chengqing.

307
00:19:01,279 --> 00:19:02,960
He was ordered

308
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:04,200
to monitor

309
00:19:04,319 --> 00:19:05,240
Chen's every move.

310
00:19:06,119 --> 00:19:08,240
Did you interrogate Wang yourself?

311
00:19:08,519 --> 00:19:09,759
He was defiant

312
00:19:10,039 --> 00:19:11,119
and refused to see me.

313
00:19:11,680 --> 00:19:12,680
Speak your mind,

314
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:13,680
my lord.

315
00:19:14,519 --> 00:19:15,519
I believe

316
00:19:16,319 --> 00:19:18,880
these two incidents

317
00:19:18,880 --> 00:19:20,720
are connected.

318
00:19:20,880 --> 00:19:23,440
They are one and the same!

319
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:25,640
If Wang truly

320
00:19:26,240 --> 00:19:27,880
sought Chen's life,

321
00:19:27,880 --> 00:19:29,680
then who has

322
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:30,359
a greater motive

323
00:19:32,039 --> 00:19:34,000
for revenge

324
00:19:34,920 --> 00:19:36,119
than Chen

325
00:19:37,519 --> 00:19:38,880
himself?

326
00:19:41,920 --> 00:19:42,720
Unthinkable...

327
00:19:43,519 --> 00:19:44,200
It has the ring of truth...

328
00:19:44,519 --> 00:19:45,359
A treacherous turn...

329
00:19:45,799 --> 00:19:46,319
Aye.

330
00:19:47,079 --> 00:19:48,039
Your Majesty,

331
00:19:48,519 --> 00:19:49,920
for an ordinary man

332
00:19:50,119 --> 00:19:51,640
to slay Wang

333
00:19:51,799 --> 00:19:53,559
would be a feat of gods.

334
00:19:53,880 --> 00:19:55,960
But Chen holds prestige rank

335
00:19:56,240 --> 00:19:57,559
and dark,

336
00:19:57,880 --> 00:19:59,000
deadly skills.

337
00:19:59,599 --> 00:20:00,759
The suspicion points

338
00:20:01,119 --> 00:20:02,960
solely at him!

339
00:20:03,359 --> 00:20:04,680
This crime is a stain upon us all.

340
00:20:05,759 --> 00:20:07,160
Your Majesty,

341
00:20:07,279 --> 00:20:08,720
let justice be

342
00:20:08,960 --> 00:20:10,039
swift and merciless!

343
00:20:17,079 --> 00:20:19,440
We implore Your Majesty,

344
00:20:19,839 --> 00:20:22,400
justice for

345
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:24,079
the fallen!

346
00:20:24,079 --> 00:20:24,599
I...
Your Majesty,

347
00:20:25,920 --> 00:20:26,839
I implore you.

348
00:20:27,319 --> 00:20:28,799
Order his arrest at once.

349
00:20:29,200 --> 00:20:30,440
To purge the rot

350
00:20:30,799 --> 00:20:33,240
from the court.

351
00:21:24,799 --> 00:21:26,880
Lord Chen has arrived!

352
00:21:51,599 --> 00:21:52,240
Greetings,

353
00:21:52,920 --> 00:21:53,960
Your Majesty!

354
00:21:55,559 --> 00:21:56,440
Rise, my lord.

355
00:21:58,960 --> 00:21:59,880
Gratitude.

356
00:22:01,359 --> 00:22:02,160
Ought you

357
00:22:02,400 --> 00:22:03,680
not be abed at home?

358
00:22:04,039 --> 00:22:05,000
Why have you come?

359
00:22:06,119 --> 00:22:06,839
Your Majesty,

360
00:22:08,319 --> 00:22:09,400
the tragedy

361
00:22:10,519 --> 00:22:12,279
of the Wangs reached me.

362
00:22:12,680 --> 00:22:13,519
I felt

363
00:22:14,039 --> 00:22:15,240
compelled to attend.

364
00:22:16,039 --> 00:22:16,839
I'd hate

365
00:22:17,319 --> 00:22:18,079
for a knife

366
00:22:18,920 --> 00:22:20,200
to be stuck

367
00:22:20,759 --> 00:22:22,160
in my back.

368
00:22:25,400 --> 00:22:27,000
The nerve of the man...

369
00:22:27,440 --> 00:22:28,559
No shame, truly...

370
00:22:30,880 --> 00:22:32,759
Spare us

371
00:22:32,759 --> 00:22:35,240
